==Death== On 7 April 2019, Afrah was found dead lying on his bed at around 9:30 (Maldivian time) after he failed to wake up for breakfast.<ref name=death/> He was pronounced dead on taking to [[Indira Gandhi Memorial Hospital]].<ref name=death/> His [[Salat al-Janazah|funeral prayer]] was performed at Aasahara Mosque after [[Isha prayer]].<ref name=death>{{cite news |url=https://www.muniavas.com/4049 |title=Actor, producer Afrah pronounced dead |language=Divehi|work=Muniavas |last=Rasheed |first=Ahmed |date=7 April 2018 |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20190406121340/https://www.muniavas.com/4049 |url-status=live|archivedate=6 April 2019 |accessdate=8 April 2019}}</ref>
